    <item>
      <title>石油价格窄幅波动，中东和库存成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商追踪中东紧张局势和温和看跌的美国库存报告，油价稳定在 3 月中旬以来的最低水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>努钦称强势美元目前有助于为美国债务融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/mnuchin-says-strong-dollar-helps-for-now-in-financing-us-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长史蒂文·姆努钦 (Steven Mnuchin) 表示，强势美元有利于美国目前为巨额财政赤字融资，但呼吁 11 月总统选举的获胜者领导一项新举措，以控制联邦债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/mnuchin-says-strong-dollar-helps-for-now-in-financing-us-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 23:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国反弹动摇，亚洲股市开盘低迷：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市低迷后，亚洲股市苦苦寻找方向，考虑到经济逆流，投资者对于市场能否维持本月的涨势存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 22:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为存在“缺货”风险，铜价触及 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/copper-advances-on-goldman-forecast-and-fed-rate-cut-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者加大了对美联储降息的押注，且高盛集团警告供应压力加剧，铜价一度突破每吨 10,000 美元。]]></description>
